6. As per the information and explanation given to us, the unsecured loan received by the Company  is purely the unsecured loan and no advance amount is received against any booking of the units.
7. This QPR Certificate as on 30/06/2022 is issued on the basis of details provided and information and explanation given to us by the management. 
8. Since B.U. Permission and all other permission was received before   i.e. 30.06.2022 and to file this QE, We have taken the data as on 30/06/2022 and the certificate is given as on 30/06/2022  as the last certificate of Form 3 was given. Only New UDIN is generated for QE Submission
